Source: includes
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Lenik <includes@bodz.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), meson, ninja-build
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: includes
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: resolve #include directives from C/C++ sources
 includes recursively parses C/C++ source files, resolves
 #include directives, evaluates conditionals, and outputs
 the list of included filenames. Suitable for Makefile
 integration and build dependency tracking.
